text: Georgian Bay Islands National Park () is a national park in Simcoe County, Ontario, Canada. The park is made up of 63 different small islands and parts of islands in Georgian Bay near Port Severn, Ontario. The largest island in the park is Beausoleil Island. ==Other websites== * Category:National parks in Canada Category:1920s establishments in Canada Category:1929 establishments in North America Category:Geography of Ontario
